@One of the most disturbing dreams that I had was when my parents were trying to kill me with a knitchen knife while running.@

@What it was scarier, is that I already know that they want me dead, so in the dream, I grabbed a tiny knife for protection.@
@I remember a talk, but I couldn't hear anything. I was just waiting.@

@After that, I started to run in all the house. In the end, I ran into the backyard of the house and got trapped there.@ 
@I tried to stop my mother by grabbing her arm and throwing the kitchen knife away.@ @I tried to use the knife that I had in one of my pockets, but I didn't want to, because they were my parents.@

@Finally, I remember falling to the floor. There was a light. Suddenly, my father appeared behind me and look at me. He started to laught. I saw my mother grabbing the knife again.@

@And I woke up@

